channel.title: Project 5 Development
channel.description:
I have been working on Project 5, a server source to be released soon, and decided to give tech specs and sneak peaks. I have made this from semi-scratch and give full credit to all server developers out there. I hope you like it, it has taken me a while, please comment!
ScreenShots:
Project 5 Home/Starting Area [img]http://exapto.com/5home.PNG[/img]
Project 5 Members Area [img]http://exapto.com/5mem.PNG[/img]
Project 5 PK Arena [img]http://exapto.com/5pk.PNG[/img]
Project 5 Barrows Area (Kinda plain) [img]http://exapto.com/5barrows.PNG[/img]
Gonna release soon! Please comment! Yes I used Galkon's Pride client for pictures (100% to him for client), but I will make a client soon =).
-Volrom
